"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-13-Chinese-Olympic-volunteers-share-memories-1vcTWPNIV3i-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Jiang Simin  Copied  Chinese volunteers are a mainstay at the Olympics. From Beijing to London, Rio to PyeongChang, and the upcoming Paris 2024, many of them have served at multiple editions of the Games. Their bright smiles and positive energy have made the experience enjoyable for both players and spectators. In this video, they share some of their Olympic memories.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"